source: crates/franken-node/tests/cli_subcommand_goldens.rs
---
franken-node: trust-native JavaScript[PATH] runtime platform

Usage: franken-node <COMMAND>

Commands:
  init        Bootstrap config, policy profile, and workspace metadata
  run         Run app under policy-governed runtime controls
  runtime     Runtime lane and epoch inspection[PATH]
  migrate     Migration audit, rewrite, and validation workflows
  verify      Compatibility verification across runtimes
  trust       Extension trust management
  remotecap   Remote capability token issuance and inspection
  trust-card  Trust-card API[PATH] parity surfaces
  fleet       Fleet control plane operations
  incident    Incident replay and forensics
  registry    Extension registry operations
  bench       Benchmark suite execution
  doctor      Diagnose environment and policy setup
  help        Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version
